{
  "id": "adv_card_kor_07_01_short",
  "title": "fran 1話 優雅な休憩も必要 (Short)",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――夏の新曲完成後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――After completing the summer new song",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "新曲用の衣装、見ましたよ。凄く良かったです\nさすがはfranさんがデザインしただけはありますね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I saw the costume for the new song. It was really good.\nAs expected from a design by fran-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_01-kor001.m4a",
      "text": "ふふん、当たり前じゃないですか\n私、自分のファッションブランドを持ってたんですよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fufu‚ of course it is.\nI had my own fashion brand‚ you know?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_01-kor002.m4a",
      "text": "そのブランド、『ERFOLG』のアイテムだって\n自分自身でデザインしていたんですから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I even designed all the items\nfor my brand‚ ERFOLG‚ myself.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_01-kor003.m4a",
      "text": "まぁ、今回は制作をかなり自由に\nやらせてもらえたから、特に自信があるんですけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ this time I was given quite a lot of freedom\nin the production‚ so I'm especially confident.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_01-kor004.m4a",
      "text": "あくまでアイドルの範囲内で大人の色気を出すことで\n他のアイドルとの差別化を図りましたし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "By showing mature charm within idol boundaries\nI aimed to differentiate us from other idols.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_01-kor005.m4a",
      "text": "素材や加工も細かく指示して、水着を模したものでも\n安っぽく見えないよう、立体感が出るようにしたんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I gave detailed instructions on materials and processing so that‚\nalthough it looks like a swimsuit‚ it has a sense of depth rather than looking cheap.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_01-kor006.m4a",
      "text": "あとは……三人それぞれのスタイルに合わせて\nディティールを考えるのも、楽しかったですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And… considering the details to match\neach of the three's styles was also fun.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_01-kor007.m4a",
      "text": "……ただ、それを着るのがmihoとkanaだって\n思うと、ちょっと癪なんですけどね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…But thinking that miho and kana\nwill wear them is a bit irritating.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.5333351135,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "な、なるほど、相当こだわり抜いたんですね\nあのクオリティも納得です。ただ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I-I see‚ you really put a lot of care into it.\nThat quality makes sense. But…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.4000017802,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}